OL,5, A former BBC radio DJ who was jailed   
OL,6, for multiple child sex offences died   
OL,7, last year, it has emerged.             
OL,9,FChris Denning, 81, became seriously ill
OL,10,Fat HMP Bedford and died in June 2022 at
OL,11,FBedford Hospital.                      
OL,13,FHis death has just come to light in a  
OL,14,FPrisons & Probation Ombudsman report,  
OL,15,Fwhich said he should have been taken to
OL,16,Fhospital more quickly.                 
OL,18,FThe prolific paedophile used his fame  
OL,19,Fto groom and sexually assault dozens of
OL,20,Fyoung victims in he 1960s, 70s and 80s.
